item.title: CVE-2018-15698|2024-09-17T01:45:38.855Z -- tenable -- asustor%20data%20master
item.description: ASUSTOR Data Master 3.1.5 and below allows authenticated remote non-administrative users to read any file on the file system when providing the full path to loginimage.cgi.

item.title: CVE-2018-15699|2024-09-17T00:05:39.085Z -- tenable -- asustor%20data%20master
item.description: ASUSTOR Data Master 3.1.5 and below makes an HTTP request for a configuration file that is vulnerable to XSS. A man in the middle can take advantage of this by inserting Javascript into the configuration files Version field.
